  "name": "Strike The Earth",
  "type": "feat",
  "effects": [],
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><span lang=\"EN\">You embody the power of the whirling sands, and call forth a raging sandstorm to envelop your foes as you strike at the earth. Spend your Zeal and Strike at a target with a groundward attack, upheaving forth sand and rock. The target and creatures adjacent to them excluding you need to make a Fortitude saving throw against your class DC or suffer a condition based on the amount of your zeal spent:</span></p><ul><li><p><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"color:black\">1-3 Zeal: Dazzled</span></p></li><li><p><span lang=\"EN\">4-5</span><span style=\"color:black\"> Zeal: Blinded</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Success </strong>The creature becomes Dazzled for 1 round.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Failure</strong> The creature becomes Dazzled or Blinded for 1 round.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Critical Failure </strong>As Failure, but creatures become Dazzled or Blinded for 2 rounds.</span></p>"
